verbose_text: In the group of clear cell RCC (ccRCC), the [18 F] FPRGD2 PET signal correlated with integrin alpha v beta 3 expression by tumor cells and IHC results confirmed high expression of alpha v beta 3 on ccRCC cells, whereas in the papillary RCC (pRCC) group, the signal correlated with integrin alpha v beta 3 level on tumor vessels XREF_BIBR.
